{"tid":703660,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿根廷應該好大壓力","createTime":"2018-06-15T20:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T03:47:51.000Z","uid":42274,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"116dd9be5b5ffe8487b273b0ed89132ba2eca1f5","tid":703660,"uid":42274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T20:16:52.000Z","msg":"先有比人睇低嘅俄羅斯炒人5粒 之後隊友so9隊烏拉圭險勝 然後提子超水準發揮 再嚟西班牙嘅超強護球能力同組織 德國嘅全面性 重有黑馬法國 <br />\n<br />\n睇番阿根廷 連基本嘅組織都冇 大部分都係靠美斯用波 喺中場死扭難扭再喂上去 提子人腳雖然名氣細 但踢起上嚟反而幾順 反而坐擁4個頂級前鋒嘅阿根廷 外圍賽場均入波兩球都冇 條中場同後防真係得啖笑 <br />\n<br />\n睇完頭幾場真係替阿根廷擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  熱門嚟講咁多隊入面最唔穩陣 美斯踢唔起真係小組賽都未必過到 不過真心想美斯c朗齊齊入16強 因為兩個都冇咩機會再踢世界杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/041438_aa0fba838231e30196d086338f8a5436.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F041438_aa0fba838231e30196d086338f8a5436.png&h=a4c85039&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/16/041439_44e40bc845de9e5d7ca1da949410498e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F16%2F041439_44e40bc845de9e5d7ca1da949410498e.png&h=dc432efe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebbbfcf5e2ac868aa7ee32918f3299324d785afa","tid":703660,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T20:20:25.000Z","msg":"阿根廷真係 成日亂鳩咁踢 唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66510fa17a79005b6b279915da777e3fb478d8d1","tid":703660,"uid":10733,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T20:25:18.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙根本攻唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e935e6ee30cc651254411c518b62eb846df84ab1","tid":703660,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T23:01:48.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯比人睇